{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2021-02-14-gatsby-redirect-from/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"18cd82f2-83ba-598d-abae-2e79ddbf1694","html":"<p>新的 Gatsby 部落格有自己一套路由設定，與原先 Hexo 不同。</p>\n<p>例如原先 Hexo 版的 <a href=\"https://www.easonchang.com/posts/scifi-trophy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">【專案】科幻風造型獎盃</a> 文章的網址是：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">https://www.easonchang.com/2018/04/04/scifi-trophy/</code></pre></div>\n<p>而將文章搬移到 Gatsby 後，網址變成了：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">https://www.easonchang.com/posts/scifi-trophy/</code></pre></div>\n<p>因為我部落格是在原網址整個重架，若有讀者將原本的網址存為書籤，再次連回來時會找不到那篇文章，因此我需要對舊文章做特殊處理，有兩種方法：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>調整 Gatsby 路由生成設定，讓舊文章維持使用舊網址（依然使用 <code class=\"language-text\">/2018/04/04/scifi-trophy/</code>）</li>\n<li>設定重導向規則，將舊網址 <code class=\"language-text\">/2018/04/04/scifi-trophy/</code> 重導向到新網址 <code class=\"language-text\">/posts/scifi-trophy/</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>我選擇走第二條路，因為我覺得新網址的比舊網址簡潔，將文章全集結到 <code class=\"language-text\">/posts</code> 路由底下，挺順眼的。</p>\n<p>而且若我未來要開新專案取名叫 <strong>2018</strong> ，想架設在 <code class=\"language-text\">https://www.easonchang.com/2018/</code> ，也可以避免路徑衝突。 </p>\n<h2 id=\"使用-gatsby-redirect-from-插件實現重導向\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-gatsby-redirect-from-%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%8D%E5%B0%8E%E5%90%91\" aria-label=\"使用 gatsby redirect from 插件實現重導向 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 gatsby-redirect-from 插件實現重導向</h2>\n<p>我找到了一個 Gatsby 的 plugin，叫做 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-redirect-from/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">gatsby-redirect-from</a> 。</p>\n<p>它的功用是可以在每篇文章的 .md 原始檔裡設定多個路徑別名，讀者用別的路徑進站時，就會被重導向到正確的文章。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/9b1e2/gatsby-redirect-from.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.08333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/8ac56/gatsby-redirect-from.webp 240w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/d3be9/gatsby-redirect-from.webp 480w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/e46b2/gatsby-redirect-from.webp 960w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/f992d/gatsby-redirect-from.webp 1440w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/17f0a/gatsby-redirect-from.webp 1880w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/8ff5a/gatsby-redirect-from.png 240w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/e85cb/gatsby-redirect-from.png 480w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/d9199/gatsby-redirect-from.png 960w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/07a9c/gatsby-redirect-from.png 1440w,\n/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/9b1e2/gatsby-redirect-from.png 1880w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ba5fad456540de9ee95197380cf2cb54/d9199/gatsby-redirect-from.png\"\n            alt=\"gatsby redirect from\"\n            title=\"gatsby redirect from\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"安裝\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D\" aria-label=\"安裝 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安裝</h3>\n<p>在終端機指令輸入下面指令安裝相關 node 套件，我使用 yarn 來安裝：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> gatsby-redirect-from gatsby-plugin-meta-redirect</code></pre></div>\n<p>然後修改 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> 檔案，啟動這兩個 plugin：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 加入下面兩行</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-redirect-from'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-meta-redirect'</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// make sure this is always the last one</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"對每篇文章設定要重導向的路徑\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%8F%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E9%87%8D%E5%B0%8E%E5%90%91%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%91\" aria-label=\"對每篇文章設定要重導向的路徑 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>對每篇文章設定要重導向的路徑</h3>\n<p>接著修改要設定重導向的文章 .md 檔。</p>\n<p>在最上方 yaml 區塊加入 <code class=\"language-text\">redirect_from</code> key，裡面是一個 array，可以針對一篇文章設定 1 到多個重導向路徑。設定完後會長這樣：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token front-matter-block\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span>\n<span class=\"token font-matter yaml language-yaml\">title: 【專案】科幻風造型獎盃\nredirect_from:\n  - /2018/04/04/scifi-trophy/</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token title important\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">##</span> 簡介</span>\n（下略...）</code></pre></div>\n<p>這樣就大功告成了！</p>\n<p>重新執行 <code class=\"language-text\">yarn deploy</code> 更新部落格後，讀者即便連到舊的文章網址，也會自動被重導向到新文章連結了！</p>\n<h2 id=\"原理\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\" aria-label=\"原理 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原理</h2>\n<p>我觀察了一下此 plugin 是如何做重導向的，發現他是在 build 完後的靜態檔裡頭，會建立多個類似下面的 <code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code> 檔，放在要被重導向的舊路徑裡（ /2018/04/04/scifi-trophy/ ）：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">http-equiv</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>refresh<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0; URL=<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>/posts/scifi-trophy/<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>用一個帶有 URL 的 refresh meta tag 來做 client-side 的重導向，content 裡的 0 代表 0 秒後要重導向，也就是立刻馬上。挺聰明的！</p>\n<p>這個方法的關鍵字是 <strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meta_refresh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Meta Refresh</a></strong> ，是滿常用的重導向實作方法，但有些瀏覽器因為安全性考量，會擋掉重導向動作，所以很多網站要做重導向時，才會同時附帶一個按鈕，說「若5秒內沒有重導向的話，請按我」。</p>\n<h2 id=\"感想\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%84%9F%E6%83%B3\" aria-label=\"感想 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>感想</h2>\n<p>這次一次性設定 30 篇舊文章的路徑，滿費工的。要一直從瀏覽器點舊文章，複製舊網址，在切換到編輯器將舊網址貼到 md 檔，並補上 redirect_from key，重複整套動作 30 次。</p>\n<p>這套流程應該要是能被自動化的，但我目前功夫還不到家，所以先手動完成了。希望以後做類似事情時，我能更像個工程師寫個小 script 自動完成它！</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2021-02-14-gatsby-redirect-from/","tagSlugs":["/tag/blog/","/tag/gatsby/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-02-14T13:23:20.292Z","description":"新的 Gatsby 部落格有自己一套路由設定，與原先 Hexo 不同。於是我使用 gatsby-redirect-from plugin 將文章舊路徑重導向。","tags":["Blog","Gatsby"],"title":"設定 Gatsby 部落格文章的舊路徑重導向，使用 gatsby-redirect-from 插件","socialImage":"./gatsby-redirect-from.png"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2021-02-14-gatsby-redirect-from/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}